  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Improved Food and Nutrition Security Improved nutrition practices in households</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ireland&apos;s support focusses on reforming the agriculture sector with a particular emphasis on improving efficiency and effectiveness through support to increasing production of nutritious non-maize crops and increasing adaptation of Climate Smart Agriculture and the promotion of livestock and biomass production. Nutrition security will be supported through treatment and prevention of under-nutrition in Dedza and Nkhata Bay Districts. Support will be provided for continuing education for nutrition staff at community level, particularly in areas such as the linkage between nutrition and food security and home fortification.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Outcome 2: Households have improved food and nutrition security</narrative>
